paragraphs:
In section 47 of the Central Goods and Services Tax Act, in sub-section (1),––
(a) the words “or inward” shall be omitted;
(b) the words and figures “or section 38” shall be omitted;
(c) after the words and figures “section 39 or section 45”, the words and figures
“or section 52” shall be inserted. 109. In section 48 of the Central Goods and Services Tax Act, in sub-section (2), the
words and figures “, the details of inward supplies under section 38” shall be omitted. 110.
